---
// Three operations cards for the landing page.
---

<div class="ops-grid">
  <div class="ops-card">
    <div class="ops-name">normalize</div>
    <p class="ops-desc">
      Left-align indels, split multi-allelic sites, and validate against a reference genome.
    </p>
    <pre class="ops-cmd">vcfkit normalize -f ref.fa input.vcf \
  &gt; normalized.vcf</pre>
    <a class="ops-link" href="/commands/normalize">Docs →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="ops-card">
    <div class="ops-name">liftover</div>
    <p class="ops-desc">
      Convert variants between genome builds using UCSC chain files. Unmapped records go to a reject file.
    </p>
    <pre class="ops-cmd">vcfkit liftover -s hg19.fa -t hg38.fa \
  -c chain.gz input.vcf</pre>
    <a class="ops-link" href="/commands/liftover">Docs →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="ops-card">
    <div class="ops-name">filter</div>
    <p class="ops-desc">
      Keep variants matching a deterministic expression — INFO fields, FORMAT fields, CHROM, POS, QUAL, FILTER.
    </p>
    <pre class="ops-cmd">vcfkit filter \
  -e "INFO/AF &lt; 0.01 &amp;&amp; FILTER == 'PASS'" \
  input.vcf</pre>
    <a class="ops-link" href="/commands/filter">Docs →</a>
  </div>
</div>
